chuan 系列、智谱 AI ChatGLM 系列、姜子牙通用大模型等。 阿里云全面升级 AI 基础设施，中国大模型公司一半跑在阿里云上！_ 业界 _ 科技频道首页 _ 财经网 - CAIJING.COM.CN"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ec6131f097e9b041b70639f453d99c0a_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/628223225"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyL+f4cLyuvAdEAMaCTEwMTg4MzkzOSCFz/SpBjAAOKABQBNyCTYyODIyMzIyNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1698754476.139158", "card_id": "Q_627743086", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待「很多人都认为自己是 ADHD」的现象？实际上 ADHD 到底有多难确诊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f80a52ec98cd81228803226dc7bea932_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627743086"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyL+f4cLyuvAdEAMaCTEwMTc3NzMwNyDAlOOpBjAAOFtAFHIJNjI3NzQzMDg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1698754476.139635", "card_id": "Q_625932565", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我想买个电脑主机接在电视上用，这样就可以免费看电视了，是否可行？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "会不会有显卡不合适的情况，有什么性价比高的推荐吗"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3a571dcc378a90f4b058b19aecd62a06_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625932565"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyL+f4cLyuvAdEAMaCTEwMTM3NTExNyCXkqOpBjAAOIUBQBVyCTYyNTkzMjU2NXgAqgEJYml